  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to generate positive changes in environmental habits of dwellers in the island of Tierra Bomba in order to improve their quality of life and help ward off plastic pollution at sea. How? By empowering local organizations, strengthening environmental education, providing technical assistance for the implementation of &quot;sustainable actions&quot; leading to better use of resources, conservation of ecosystems and biodiversity, better residue management, separation at source and recycling</narrative>
